00:35:24.960 --> 00:35:27.810
800 pages goes over the cloud.

00:35:27.810 --> 00:35:31.420
&gt;&gt; Jo Reed: Goes through the cloud.

00:35:31.420 --> 00:35:34.320
&gt;&gt; Julia Glass: And she is
